 rency and bullish for bonds.\n\n• Why traders care: Central-bank decis
 ions directly affect interest rates\, currency valuation\, bond yields a
 nd equity risk appetite.\n\n• Frequency: Scheduled several times per y
 ear.\n\n• Notes: The market often reacts not only to the rate decision
 \, but also to the statement\, forecasts\, press conference and tone.\n\
 n• Acronyms: FOMC = Federal Open Market Committee\; RBA = Reserve Bank
